      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, trim the <strong>green stalk<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong> from the <strong>aubergine<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong> and cut into quarters lengthways&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a high heat</p>\r\n<p>Once hot, add the<strong> aubergine</strong> and cook for 2 min on each flesh side until browned</p>\r\n<p>Transfer the <strong>aubergine</strong> to the tray with the&nbsp;<strong>sweet potato</strong>&nbsp;and return it to the oven for 15-20 min</p>",
