      "instruction": "<p>Add 300ml <span class=\"text-danger\">[500ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong> to the pan, then add the <strong>soy sauce</strong>, <strong>mango chutney</strong> and <strong>nigella seeds</strong></p>\r\n<p>Whisk to combine and cook for 5-7 min or until the sauce has thickened &ndash; this is your <strong>curry sauce</strong></p>\r\n<p>Meanwhile, trim then slice the <strong>spring onions</strong>&nbsp;finely</p>\r\n<p>Bash the <strong>roasted peanuts</strong> with a <strong>rolling pin</strong> until finely crushed (keep them in the bag so you don't lose any!)</p>",
